C.2 Causal Step

```
Input: q_prev, q_curr
Output: q_next

q_next = 2*q_curr - q_prev
for iter = 1..max_iters:
    F = D2 L(q_prev, q_curr) + D1 L(q_curr, q_next)
    if ||F|| < tol: break
    J = D1 D2 L(q_curr, q_next)
    solve J Δ = -F
    q_next += Δ
